pr_body:
This PR contains an implementation for the DeepSDF, which can represent a shape's surface by a continuous Signed Distance Function(SDF) representation, and enables high quality shape representation, interpolation and completion from partial and noisy 3D input data. The implementation is based on the original implementation in PyTorch and I rewrite them to TensorFlow 2.0 codes. You can basically execute these codes in the same way as the original implementation.

I have no confidence in how to write LICENSE. Could anyone please check it?

The implementation is based on the original implementation in PyTorch and I rewrite them to TensorFlow 2.0 codes. You can basically execute these codes in the same way as the original implementation.
